  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, we score each combination using the Bi-Label Document Scorer and generate two scores and only select the sub-documents combinations whose scores are located on the skyline.",
    "(2) Feature Engineering.",
    "For each combination, we concatenate the two scores of all its sub-documents and pad with zeros at the end to maintain the same total input length; (3) Labeling.",
    "We concatenate each sub-documents combination with the question and input it to Llama2-13B-Chat.",
    "If Llama generates the correct answer, the sub-documents combination is labeled as 1; otherwise, it is labeled as 0."
